description: Leigh interviewed the late and great Mose Allison many times over the decades.  By the 1990's they got into an interview routine that included Mose giving a short review of whatever book(s) he was reading.  This one is from June 10, 2006 at which time Leigh was nearing the end his career as a broadcaster.
title: Mose Allison June 2006
